=== Noun ===
'''smoke''' (''[[uncountable]] and [[countable]]''; ''plural'' [[smokes]])

#(''[[uncountable]]'') Very fine [[particle]]s and [[vapor]]/[[vapour]] given off by [[burn]]ing material.
#An instance of [[smoking]] a [[cigarette]], [[cigar]], etc.
#:''I'm going out to have a smoke.''
#(''slang'') A [[cigarette]].
#(colour) a light grey colour, tinted with blue.
#:<table><tr><td>smoke colour: &nbsp;</td><td bgcolor="#D6E2E2" width="80">&nbsp; </td></tr></table>

